title: Total number of retail prescriptions filled annually in the U.S. 2013 to 2025
yAxis: Number of prescriptions filled in billions
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of prescriptions filled in billions, containing a total of 13 data points.
In general Number of prescriptions filled in billions has rose over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2015 and 2016.
Maximum Number of prescriptions filled in billions, about 4.98 was reported at Year 2025
The lowest Number of prescriptions filled in billions, of value 4.07 was reported at Year 2016
